'''Medigeshi''' or '''Midigeshi''' is a village in [[Madhugiri]] Taluk, [[Tumkur]] district in [[Karnataka]], [[India]]. It has a population of 2,649 according to 2011 census.<ref> https://www.census2011.co.in/data/village/610685-medigeshi-karnataka.html </ref> The village has a fort which is a tourist attraction.<ref> http://jlrexplore.com/explore/natural-areas/medigeshi-a-fort-guards-nature </ref>

